zwnj = 200c
zwj = 200d 


to have ta-hashanto-ta you would have

ta+hashanto+zwj+ta

to have khanda-ta + ta you would have

ta+hashanto+zwnj+ta

and to have ta-y-ta (the conjunct)

ta+hashanto+ta


> ra+hasonto+(a consonant) = reph form (as is current)
> ra+hashonto+zwj+ontestojaw = ra-y-jawphola <--- proposed change
> xx+ontestojaw = xx+jawphola (as is current)


